description: Details of all reserved matters (Access, Appearance, Landscaping, Layout and Scale) pursuant to outline planning permission ref PA/13/02966 dated 24/12/2014 relating to the following areas of the Wood Wharf Masterplan:  i. Development Plots A1, A4, B3 ii. Ground and above ground infrastructure, streets, structures, open spaces, landscaping and public realm within Part of Development Zones A, B, D and K iii. Ground a d above ground infrastructure, streets, open spaces, landscaping and public realm outside Development Zones A, B, D and K but linked to i and ii above.   Comprising 483 private residential units (Class C3), 10,726 sqm (GIA) of business accommodation (Class B1), 1,907 sqm (GIA) of retail, leisure and community uses (A1-A5, D1 and D2), 1,780 sqm of ancillary circulation space; as well as associated infrastructure, streets, open spaces, landscaping, public realm, parking, servicing, utilities and other associated works.
